These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, crime, romance, zombie
1. the person watching crime movies is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching zombie movies##2
2. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | zombie | crime | romance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, grapefruit, kiwi, zucchini
1. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
2. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating lime##1
3. the person eating zucchini is between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating lime##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Food   | grapefruit | zucchini | lime | kiwi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, lawyer, nurse, writer
1. the writer is on the right of the accountant##1
