2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Sport   | water-polo | volleyball | weightlifting | badminton |

 